data.message: All of you trying to put together a movement to bring back the beefy crunch burrito need to get your priorities straight. Why bring back a king when you bring back A GOD. #XXLCHALUPA #askforsomethingyoucantactuallymakeyourselfdumdum
Ya know, I see a lotta complaints on this page. "Beefy crunch" this, "bring back" that. You know what *I* miss from Taco Bell? Black friggin' Olives.
This is a better logo. Love the new one don't get me wrong but I like this one better :) #beefycrunchmovement
They can never get your order right. They have screwed up my order three times in a row. They will never get it right, because I will never go back again. Good riddance!
Low key I know this isn't your thing but all you guys are missing is fries and I will alwayssssss go to Taco Bell. Keep innovating and coming up with new stuff. We will keep buying haha

Waited inside the resturant with about 7 other tables with people at them for approximately 45 minutes for our food Tuesday evening and then when we got it, it was horrible! I mean really??? I ordered beef meximelts, no peco, with sour cream! How hard is that?? Its bad enough they used to be 99cents and now they are what?? over two bucks?? and then you get them and they are half slapped together and the crap is all running out the edges and then ends...well never again...and I will tell everyone I know....It reminds me why people say the never eat at taco bell unless they are drunk and leaving the bar!! Thats about the only time you can stomach that kind of food/service!

You have to be kidding me!  Is it April Fools Day? This is supposed to be a bean and cheese burrito.  NO cheese and barely any beans. All tortilla!  I could have just eaten a slice of bread at home. Sad that the managers are not teaching the workers how to properly make the food.  Last visit!

I'd be happy if at our local taco bell here in Stillwater Oklahoma  if you could get your employees to wash their hands before leaving the bathroom it would also be helpful to have soap and paper towels in the bathroom

Absolutely the worst customer service ever! And way to go new owner shut both of your restaurants down at the same time,  didn't update your website, didn't shut your lights off to say closed and let me use the app to order my food... can't get much worse then that

Im at the taco Bell now in Amelia placed my order at 837 still haven't got it I'm the only customer only seen 4 cars in the drive thru manager outside smoking when I got here still out there I think the cashier has his drive thru headset on and headphones on from his cell phone  he took my order and is hanging out with his buddies in the dinning room I think they have the air conditioning on and the dinning room is a mess
That purple could use a little complimentary red! #BeefyCrunchBurrito #BeefyCrunchMovement

I think all these "fans" of the beefy crunch that constantly spam every facebook post with pictures of the burrito and hashtags are really taco bell employees to drive up demand. They are just ads. Hundreds of these comments on every single post. These are either employees  or bots.

Hey Taco Bell, how about putting the ingredients in the burritos evenly so I don't get a mouthful of nacho cheese, a mouthful of beans, a mouthful of rice and a mouthful of chipotle mayo. It's nasty, and 8/10 burritos I've had lately have been nasty.
Bring back Chili cheese burrito and Baja sauce you jerks. Messing up a good thing. Spicy ranch is horrible who eats warm ranch? Blech.
